log
@use bu_file_exists() instead of access()
@
text
@/*                      P I X - O R L E . C
 * BRL-CAD
 *
 * Copyright (c) 1986-2007 United States Government as represented by
 * the U.S. Army Research Laboratory.
 *
 * This program is free software; you can redistribute it and/or
